  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Will fuel prices drop today?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister Kanchana Wijesekara has said that there will be no reduction in the fuel price today (01) as per the price formula.",
        "He mentioned this while addressing the budget debate in Parliament today.",
        "I don't believe fuel prices will go down with that revision, especially at today's import prices.",
        "However, we hope that the people will get that relief when the refinery is fully operational in the future, he said. (R)"
      ],
